<div>

<p source="SHANGBO.ZHONGGONG 3.11.3 (STRIPS 2, 5) JI XUSHENG 3: 177"><pb xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-1a" ed="tls" n="001-1a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-1a.1">[...] 與聞之,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-1a.2">夫季氏, 河東之盛家也,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-1a.3">亦以行矣,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-1a.4">為之宗,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-1a.5">誨汝.」</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.ZHONGGONG 3.11.1 (STRIPS 1, 4, 26) JI XUSHENG 3: 176-177"><pb xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-2a" ed="tls" n="001-2a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-2a.1">季桓使仲弓為宰</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-2a.2">仲弓以告孔子</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-2a.3">曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-2a.4">季氏[…]使雍也</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-2a.5">從於宰夫之後,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-2a.6">雍也憧愚,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-2a.7">恐貽吾子羞,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-2a.8">愿因吾子而 辭.」</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.ZHONGGONG 3.11.2 (STRIPS 26-3) JI XUSHENG 3: 177"><pb xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-3a" ed="tls" n="001-3a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-3a.1">孔子曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-3a.2">「雍[汝] [...]</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-3a.3">[夫]子有臣萬人導汝,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-3a.4">使老其家,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-3a.5">夫 [...]</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.ZHONGGONG 3.11.4 (STRIPS 5, 7-8) JI XUSHENG 3: 177"><pb xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-4a" ed="tls" n="001-4a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-4a.1">仲弓曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-4a.2">「敢問為政何先?」</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-4a.3">老老</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-4a.4">慈幼,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-4a.5">先有司,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-4a.6">舉賢才,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-4a.7">宥過</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-4a.8">舉罪.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-4a.9">[...]罪, 政之始也.」</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.ZHONGGONG 3.11.5 (STRIPS 8, 14, 9)JI XUSHENG 3: 177"><pb xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-5a" ed="tls" n="001-5a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-5a.1">仲弓曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-5a.2">「若夫老老老老</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-5a.3">慈幼,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-5a.4">既聞命矣.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-5a.5">夫先有司為之</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-5a.6">如何?」</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-5a.7">仲尼曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-5a.8">「夫民安舊</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-5a.9">而重遷</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-5a.10">造變不行,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-5a.11">委蛇 (?) (9) 有成,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-5a.12">是故有司不可不先也.」</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.ZHONGGONG 3.11.6 (STRIPS 9-10) JI XUSHENG 3: 177"><pb xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-6a" ed="tls" n="001-6a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-6a.1">仲弓曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-6a.2">「雍也不敏,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-6a.3">雖有賢才,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-6a.4">弗知舉也.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-6a.5">敢問舉才 (10) 如之何?」</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-6a.6">仲尼:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-6a.7">「夫賢才不可弇也.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-6a.8">舉爾所知,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-6a.9">爾所不知,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-6a.10">人其舍之者.」</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.ZHONGGONG 3.11.7 (STRIPS 10, 28, 19)JI XUSHENG 3: 177"><pb xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-7a" ed="tls" n="001-7a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-7a.1">仲弓曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-7a.2">「宥過赦罪,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-7a.3">則民何後?</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-7a.4">仲尼曰 [?]</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-7a.5">山有崩,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-7a.6">川有竭,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-7a.7">日月星辰猶差,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-7a.8">民亡不有過,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-7a.9">賢者 [...]</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.ZHONGGONG 3.11.8 (STRIPS 27, 15, 18) JI XUSHENG 3: 178"><pb xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-8a" ed="tls" n="001-8a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-8a.1">仲弓曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-8a.2">「敢問民務.」</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-8a.3">孔子曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-8a.4">「善哉,問乎!</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-8a.5">足以教矣,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-8a.6">君[...] 毋自惰也.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-8a.7">昔三代之明王有四海之內,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-8a.8">猶徠 [...]</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.ZHONGGONG 3.11.9 (STRIPS 6, 23B, 23A) JI XUSHENG 3: 178"><pb xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-9a" ed="tls" n="001-9a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-9a.1">「雍,汝知者(=之).」</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-9a.2">仲弓答曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-9a.3">「雍也弗聞也.」</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-9a.4">孔子曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-9a.5">「夫祭,至敬之本也,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-9a.6">所以立生也,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-9a.7">不可不慎也;</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-9a.8">夫喪至愛之卒也,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-9a.9">所以成死也,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-9a.10">不可不慎也;</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-9a.11">夫行,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-9a.12">巽求學</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-9a.13">[...]刑政不緩,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-9a.14">德教不倦.」</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.ZHONGGONG 3.11.10 (STRIPS 11, 13)JI XUSHENG 3: 178"><pb xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-10a" ed="tls" n="001-10a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-10a.1">仲弓曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-10a.2">「若此三者,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-10a.3">聞命矣,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-10a.4">敢問道民興德如何?」</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-10a.5">孔子曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-10a.6">「申之服之,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-10a.7">緩弛而遜力之.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-10a.8">雖有愆德, 其 [...]</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.ZHONGGONG 3.11.11 (STRIPS 12, 22) JI XUSHENG 3: 178-179"><pb xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-11a" ed="tls" n="001-11a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-11a.1">[...] 也廢,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-11a.2">不及其成.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-11a.3">獨主厭人,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-11a.4">難為從正.」</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-11a.5">孔子曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-11a.6">「雍,古之事君者,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-11a.7">以忠與敬,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-11a.8">雖其難也,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-11a.9">汝惟以 [...]</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.ZHONGGONG 3.11.12 (STRIPS 22, 24, 25) JI XUSHENG 3: 179"><pb xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-12a" ed="tls" n="001-12a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-12a.1">[...] 上下相報以忠,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-12a.2">則民歡承教,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-12a.3">害[.]者不 [...]</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-12a.4">[...] 之.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-12a.5">一日以善蒞,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-12a.6">所教皆終;</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-12a.7">一日以不善蒞,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-12a.8">所教皆崩,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-12a.9">可不慎乎?」</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.ZHONGGONG 3.11.13 (STRIPS 25, 20) JI XUSHENG 3: 179"><pb xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-13a" ed="tls" n="001-13a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-13a.1">仲弓曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-13a.2">「今之君子使人,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-13a.3">不盡其悅 [...]</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-13a.4">[...] 其咎.」[...]</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-13a.5">仲弓曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-13a.6">「今之君子,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-13a.7">愎過捍析,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-13a.8">難以納諫.」</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.ZHONGGONG 3.11.14 (STRIPS 20, 16A) JI XUSHENG 3: 179"><pb xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-14a" ed="tls" n="001-14a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-14a.1">孔子曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-14a.2">「今之君 [...]</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-14a.3">[...] 宜順(?)之至者,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-14a.4">教而使之,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-14a.5">君子亡所厭人.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-14a.6">今汝相夫子所,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-14a.7">竭其情,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-14a.8">盡其慎者,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-14a.9">三害近務(?) 矣.」</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.ZHONGGONG 3.11.15 (Appended strip) JI XUSHENG 3: 179"><pb xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-15a" ed="tls" n="001-15a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-15a.1">[...]飪(?).」</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-15a.2">孔子曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-15a.3">「唯政者,正也.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-15a.4">夫子雖有舉,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-15a.5">汝獨正之,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-15a.6">豈不有匡也.」</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0041_tls_001-15a.7">仲 [...]</seg></p>

